# Bash Language & Syntax Cheat Sheet

## ------------------------------ Variables

### Simple

myvar="toto"

echo $myvar

### With command

variable=$(command)
variable=$(command [option] arg1 arg2 ... )
variable=$(/path/to/binary)

variable=`command`
variable=`command [option] arg1 arg2 `
variable=`/path/to/binary`


